###############################################################################
# resilience-lab — 20: ciclo de vida do pacote (package-service :8081)
# A roteirização é ASSÍNCRONA (janela nominal ~2–6s): após criar/alterar, aguarde
# e reconsulte até o status virar ROUTE_CALCULATED. Execute de cima para baixo.
# IntelliJ: ambiente "lab" (requests/http-client.env.json).
#
# Os caos do lab que passam pelo SQS (reentrega do mesmo eventId, route.calculated
# forjado com destinationCep antigo, mensagem poison) não são expressáveis em
# .http — são os scripts scenarios/02..05. Aqui fica só a parte HTTP dos fluxos.
###############################################################################
@packageHost = http://localhost:8081

### [Feliz] Criar pacote Blumenau (89010000) → Joinville (89201000) — ambos com hub no seeder
# @name labPacote
POST {{packageHost}}/api/v1/packages
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "senderCep": "89010000",
  "recipientCep": "89201000",
  "weight": 2.5,
  "description": "resilience-lab: fluxo feliz"
}

> {% client.global.set("labPackageId", response.body.id); %}

### [Feliz] Consultar (repita até status = ROUTE_CALCULATED, com routeInfo preenchido)
GET {{packageHost}}/api/v1/packages/{{labPackageId}}

### [Feliz] Listar pacotes
GET {{packageHost}}/api/v1/packages

### [Feliz] Filtrar por status
GET {{packageHost}}/api/v1/packages?status=ROUTE_CALCULATED

# ─────────── Mudança de destino (base do cenário 04-stale-route) ───────────

### [Feliz] Mudar o destino para São Paulo (01310100) — pacote volta a ROUTE_PENDING
# e, após o recálculo assíncrono, retorna a ROUTE_CALCULATED com a rota nova.
# É neste intervalo que o cenário 04 injeta o route.calculated stale via SQS.
PATCH {{packageHost}}/api/v1/packages/{{labPackageId}}/destination
Content-Type: application/json

{ "newCep": "01310100" }

### Reconsultar (aguarde ~2–6s; recipientCep = 01310100, rota recalculada)
GET {{packageHost}}/api/v1/packages/{{labPackageId}}

# ─────────────────────── Avanço de status ───────────────────────

### [Feliz] ROUTE_CALCULATED → IN_TRANSIT (só após a rota calculada)
PATCH {{packageHost}}/api/v1/packages/{{labPackageId}}/status
Content-Type: application/json

{ "packageId": "{{labPackageId}}", "newStatus": "IN_TRANSIT" }

### [Feliz] IN_TRANSIT → DELIVERED (estado terminal — nada transiciona a partir dele)
PATCH {{packageHost}}/api/v1/packages/{{labPackageId}}/status
Content-Type: application/json

{ "packageId": "{{labPackageId}}", "newStatus": "DELIVERED" }

# ─────────────────── Falhas conhecidas (tratadas) ───────────────────

### [Falha 400] CEP inválido (menos de 8 dígitos)
POST {{packageHost}}/api/v1/packages
Content-Type: application/json

{ "senderCep": "123", "recipientCep": "89201000", "weight": 2.5 }

### [Falha 400] Peso não positivo
POST {{packageHost}}/api/v1/packages
Content-Type: application/json

{ "senderCep": "89010000", "recipientCep": "89201000", "weight": 0 }

### [Falha 400] Campo obrigatório ausente (recipientCep)
POST {{packageHost}}/api/v1/packages
Content-Type: application/json

{ "senderCep": "89010000", "weight": 2.5 }

### Pacote para os testes de transição inválida
# @name labPacoteInvalido
POST {{packageHost}}/api/v1/packages
Content-Type: application/json

{ "senderCep": "89010000", "recipientCep": "89201000", "weight": 1.0, "description": "resilience-lab: transicao invalida" }

> {% client.global.set("labPkgInvalido", response.body.id); %}

### [Falha 422] Transição inválida: pulo direto para DELIVERED (invariante I1 na borda HTTP)
PATCH {{packageHost}}/api/v1/packages/{{labPkgInvalido}}/status
Content-Type: application/json

{ "packageId": "{{labPkgInvalido}}", "newStatus": "DELIVERED" }

### [Falha 400] Corpo sem packageId (validação exige packageId + newStatus)
PATCH {{packageHost}}/api/v1/packages/{{labPkgInvalido}}/status
Content-Type: application/json

{ "newStatus": "IN_TRANSIT" }

### [Falha 404] Pacote inexistente
GET {{packageHost}}/api/v1/packages/000000000000000000000000
